      "name": "FDA generic pump hemolysis validation — 5 operating points",
      "description": "Predicted hemolysis index compared against in-vitro measurements at all five flow-speed operating points. Mean absolute error 8.3%; all predictions within two experimental standard deviations. Monte Carlo UQ bounds confirmed to bracket experimental observations in 4 of 5 cases. Screening sensitivity study referenced in UQ report section 4.2 identified inlet flow rate and rotational speed as dominant variance contributors, each accounting for >30% of output variance; remaining parameters collectively contribute <15%."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/vad-hemolysis-val-result-002",
