      "name": "Mesh convergence and discretization error characterization",
      "description": "Richardson extrapolation performed on three systematically refined meshes (4.2M, 12.6M, 37.8M cells). Grid convergence index (GCI) for hemolysis index below 3.1% at all operating points. Iterative convergence confirmed via residual monitoring to 1e-6."
    }
  ],
