      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence and hemolysis constitutive model selection must be justified relative to available alternatives with documented basis for choice at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on comparative study against k-epsilon and LES for rotating blood pump geometries. Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis power-law model used; comparison against Bludszuweit model documented with <5% difference in NIH. Model form uncertainty estimated and included in Monte Carlo UQ. Achieved level 4 meets required level 4."
