      "rationale": "Direct correspondence established between experimental boundary conditions and simulation inputs for all five operating points. Fluid property measurements at test temperature matched to simulation material properties. Rotational speed encoder accuracy ±0.5 RPM; inlet flow Coriolis meter accuracy ±0.3%. All discrepancies quantified and incorporated into Monte Carlo input distributions. Achieved level 4 meets required level 4."
